Use my code: emily25 to get 25% off your order! Discount active for 1 week only! #onceuponapp

5 tips for my aspiring FB Marketplace addicts 🤎. 

1. Use search words. The more descriptive you are, the better the chances of finding what your looking for.
2. Try increasing and decreasing your search radius for more options 
3. “Saving” items you like, even if you don’t plan on buying them, will tell the algorithm you want to see more like it!
4. When you find something you love, write the seller a personalized note! They’re more likely to respond. 
5. Patience! A true treasure may take some time to find, but it’s always worth the wait. 

You can get more tips and details on the werethewhites.com 🤎

The secret’s out of the bag🤫🧳

Today I published our 2024 project list which I includes a secret we’ve been keeping: we bought a beach cottage!

Located in Lakeside, Michigan — a place near and dear to my heart — the plan is to renovate the cottage over the next few years and transform it into the Airbnb of our dreams.  First up: the exterior! Stay tuned for all the plans we have to give this sweet, little cottage the refresh it deserves ✨🏡🤎 can’t wait to bring you along!
